      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs perfectly. It's truly in pristine condition, inside and out. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I've priced it to move. You're going to love driving this beauty!",
