    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S54B32 power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing system to achieve a remarkable 100hp-per-liter output. The drivetrain features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox linked to a variable M-differential lock for optimal power delivery. This chassis has undergone rigorous inspection with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive preventative maintenance overhaul, including rod bearing replacement. The suspension retains its factory-engineered kinematics with fresh bushings, ensuring the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. Every aspect of the mechanical assembly remains in peak operational condition, free of parasitic loss or thermal inefficiency.",
